Data-Formatter-Text version 1.0
================================

This module that converts Perl data structures into formatted text,
much like Data::Dumper, except for that it formats the data nicely
for presentation to a human. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Attribute::Abstract
 Scalar::Util
 List::Util
 List::MoreUtils
 Roman	

